uid":244110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T18:32:12.000Z","msg":"到底幾時先好返"},{"pid":"4be55a76bb3cc051aebf0107d53197cad2a55149","tid":2060504,"uid":243978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T18:46:12.000Z","msg":"以最基本就覺得你先要搵人傾 有人陪 改變一些唔好既想法 <br />\n例如 參加一些活動呀 或一齊藍球又好 一齊出去散步跑步又好 <br />\n另外搵d好既興趣 培一培養 例如 唱歌 跳舞 學拳<br />\n其實覺得情緒精神病最需要就係親人朋友既陪伴 如果唔係跟本好難捱 唉<br />\n而且盡量唔好咁晚訓啦"},{"pid":"b36b308044ac31ad593be108f39ae859c8649e2a","tid":2060504,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T19:32:15.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0t%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=25d5a64c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/archives/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2Farchives%2F2&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0t%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=68ee897c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/archives/2</a>"},{"pid":"f6d7d1b1e6059ac66fbfcf2f7b7928c96e79f671","tid":2060504,"uid":360404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T19:34:41.000Z","msg":"有，強迫症好辛苦，內心長時間存於struggling, 乜都做唔到"},{"pid":"2122cb1b2bc05583044753e0f57117d5220f89bb","tid":2060504,"uid":307183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T19:36:21.000Z","msg":"有 成日失眠 訓得差真係好大影響"},{"pid":"22762a1e3056e46ee22666684222fe939cd01410","tid":2060504,"uid":243872,"like":0,"dislike"